    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, then chop them finely and discard the stems</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and grate the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Soak the <strong>skewers</strong> in<strong> cold water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1594052433617-x200.jpg",
