    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric </strong>and<strong> chopped mint</strong> in a bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Squeeze in the juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and season with a very generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>herby marinade</strong></p>",
